{"tid":688843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日檔案 30歲大波人妻少婦 要求讓座","createTime":"2018-06-03T14:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T08:57:25.000Z","uid":99568,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"855e026b366a414ce8881daf6dc969c7d5748990","tid":688843,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BXpjZxLZM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBXpjZxLZM5Q&d=hpq7ZA7EHjIIdPpRstEu%2FJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6a51fa6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BXpjZxLZM5Q</a><br />\n12分50秒 開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁嘅人妻 咁嘅八婆格 真係好想 係咁懲罰佢, 下次地鐵 冇曬位我會叫佢坐大髀 係咁un佢屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea30d6c5af5cbf018f93cf69682fc57f39983cc2","tid":688843,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61bfc8623d7ce25e1c791065c0c050fba0f3a17a","tid":688843,"uid":99568,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"條女真係好撚索呀!!! 好想廝開佢條裙，一手扯撚爛佢條底褲 !!! 一口吸落去佢隻美鮑仔度係咁吸啜!!! 條利伸到最盡把佢陰道內所有蜜汁同閪屎全部奶乾淨!!! 連佢閪邊o的油都要奶埋!!! 兩隻手大大吸手狂搾佢對大波,食指同中指用70%力夾佢奶頭!!! 再轉身放條巨撚入佢個口度!!!頂佢吊鐘!!望住佢流眼淚個樣時， 再轉身用100%力度一野屌落佢個淫閪度!!! 之後插完屎窿!!!!再插佢個口迫佢食返自己o的屎!!! 屌緊佢個口時,用三條手指插入佢個閪度係咁了!!! 最後插到個閪最盡射精!!一定要搞大佢個肚!!!"},{"pid":"3fabb6642790ab4cd15cc19afcab79a1e63f243e","tid":688843,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ccdbc05b7a08b59d3f6406d606f9dc37554f970c","tid":688843,"uid":99568,"like":8,"dislike":16,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/230057_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.e